steps.description:
* Accept Quest in front of you
* go into Den (Cave) on your Left 
* Turn in And Accept Next Quest

* Kill Boar until LVL 2
* Go To Quest

* Accept Quest
* Kill Named Scorpion: Sarkoth
* Go Back same way
* Turn in Sarkoth Quest
* Accept next Part Quest

* Kill all remaining Boars
* Finish, Go Back To Village 
* Go In Den (Cave)
steps.tips:
If no Boars here:
* South is also a spot

steps.description:
* Go Out And Left (Cooking Area), Accept Quest
* Sell all your stuff
* Go To your Class Trainer
* Move to the Wagon, Accept Vile Familiars
* Move to the Tree, Accept Lazy Peon

* Walk To the Lazy Peon (BLUE)
* Kill every Scorpion 
* Kill every Familiar
* Loot The Apple from the cactuses
steps.tips: * If possible try all Familiars at once so you don't must back

steps.description:
* Turn In Quest
* Turn Quest at Cooking Area In
* Sell your Items!!!
* GO in Den
* Go to your Class teacher lean new spells (if necessary)
* Go to the wagon
* Go to the Tree
Go In the Cave

* Move Right ways in Cave
* Kill Yarrog Baneshadow (Orc) for the Medallion
* Jump Down Hold Rightways
* walk the water steam up ways 
* at the waterSource you will find the Pick Axe

* HearthStone Back

* Turn In Quest At Wagon + Accept New Quest
* Turn In Quest At Tree

* LEAVE NOOB ZONE!

* Go To Sen'Jin Village
* Search for A Moving NPC infront
(maybe behind the tree or the rocks)
* Accept All Quests in Village
* Move Back To the Road (Road Signs)
* Accept Quest

* Run North To Razor Hill
* Grind off the road
steps.tips:
* if u play in a Group, kill the Barron and Loot the chest for one, 
* Jump Down, and grind your way to Razor Hill

steps.description:
* Turn in and Accept Quest on the Bunker (in and out)
* Go to Wagon accept Quest
* move up to the watchtower Accept quest
* jump Down, Go to the Inn-Keeper Turn in / Accept Quest
* MAKE RAZOR HILL TO YOUR HOME
* Go To the Baracks learn First Aid
* Leave Razor Hill to Southways
steps.tips:
* You can Split up (only one person must go up to the watchTower) SHARE QUEST
* the other one can accept first aid

steps.description:
* Kill all Humans at the Castle 
* Loot Canvas Scraps
* Move While Killing in the Castle (Keep Right)
* Kill Lieutenant Benedict (get his Key)
* Go back in the Hall (not Downstairs) straight forward Go Up.
* Loot Chest + ACCEPT LETTER ITEM QUEST
* Jump of the Wall
* Kill all Missing Mobs and Loot
* Die and Release Rez at ghost Healer!
steps.tips: Lieutenant Benedict is a double PULL, be careful!

steps.description:
* GO To Bunker, Turn In 2 Quest Accept next Parts
* Go Up To the Watch Tower Turn In.
* Leave Razor Hill to the South East To the Water (ShipWracks)

* Go into the water Look for the ToolBoxes (BLUE)
* Kill The Big Makrura and LOOT
* kill the little Crawler and LOOT
* GO STRAIGHT West, Cross the Road
steps.tips:
REMEMBER TO BREATH!
Try to swim in a big loop so there is no respwan Problems

steps.description:
* Kill all 4 QuilBoar AND Scouts
* Go SOUTH To Troll Village Sen'Jin

* Go South To The Kalkar 
* You can Grind if u want

* Burn the 3 Attack Plans Down (Lay on Ground)
* Kill Kolkars
* Go To Sen'Jin Village

* Turn In Quests at Sen'Jin Village
* Go To Echo Isles
steps.tips: * Mage Trainer is in Town

steps.description:
* Look For the Purple Egg Nests on the Ground (BLUE)
* Kill every Tiger 
* on Main Isle Go Look for Zalazane (walk on ramp) Kill Him and Loot Head
* Up this Ramp (Hill) is a heap of Skulls, LOOT ONE! 
* Kill The Trolls on the Center Island and North
* Go Back To SenJin to turn Quest in.
steps.tips:
* Try to avoid Raptors (if you don't want to grind)
* You can DIE on purpose (then Res) if U finish all Quests.

steps.description:
* Turn in 3 Quests Quests
* Use HearthStone to Razor Hills

* Turn In Quest
* Resupply and Repair 
* Go West

* Kill Razormane DustRunner AND BattleGuards
* Grind Your way North if Quest is Done!

* Accept Quest In House
* Go North And Accept Goblin Quest on the Street
* Go Back South and fight through harpy 
* LOOT BAGS on the ground (BLUE) 
* Turn In Quest by Goblin
steps.tips: * GRIND until ~65% Exp

steps.description:
* Go through the Tunnel and Kill harpies
* Turn in Quest At Goblin 
* Go West
* KEEP GRINDING until Hit at least Level 9 with 92% (1,5 bars)

* Grind your way until u hit at least LVL 10 
* Find Quest between Rocks, Accept (Don't Worry its Plenty of Time.)
* Go to OG

* GO STRAIGHT to your Class Trainer! (Ask a guard) 
* Accept your Class Quest
* Go To Thrall Accept Quest 
* Next to Him Turn in and get next Part
* Go to Cleft of Shadow (RageFire Entrance, NOT IN THE INSTANCE)
* on the Right Side find Troll With an Antidote Quest
* Leave Ogrimmar
steps.tips: * From Now on the Need a Cure Timer is not important...

steps.description:
* Right (West) and Kill Scorpions if
* All Scorpions Down? Go to the River in Kill Crocodiles until the Amulet Drops.
* Farm Scorpions until u have 4 Poison Sacs
* Go South to the Canyon Entrance (Or Jump Down)
* Kill Fizzle Goblin (Loot Claw)
* Go out of the Canyon!
steps.tips: * Before enter the Canyon, Warrior accept Class quest! (bridge Barrens)

steps.description:
* Go East to the Small House 
* Turn in Amulet Quest
* Go To Razor hill
* Accept Quest at West Entrance
* Turn in Quest in Front of the Bunker AND accept new One
steps.tips:
* At This Point maybe Try your Class quest
If Ready use HS to Port back after this to Razor Hill

steps.description:
* GO To Margot North
* you can Grind if u want

* Go Into the Cave
* keep always LEFT 
* try to find Ganz'uz (lvl 14) Drops Quest
* Accept DropQuest
* Leave Cave
* Turn in Quest
* Go to Ogrimmar

* GO To Thrall
* GO To the Cleft of Shadow
* Turn in Antidote (Troll Right Side)
* Turn in Quests in Tent in front of RageFire Entrance
* After Turn in all Quest and Accept new one
* SPEAK WITH NPC (SPEAK BUBBLE)
* Return To Thrall, Turn in Quest and Accept new One
* Leave Ogrimmar
steps.tips:
* You have Now 2 Rage Fire Quests
* If HS rdy use it to port to RazorHill / otherwise walk

steps.description:
* Go East 
* Cancel Quest "Need for a Cure"
* reAccept Quest AND Turn In.
* Leave Durotar 
* Go over the River there is a Street follow street South Ways
* Turn in Quest in front of the Bunker / Accept New
* Under The Tower Turn in Quest / Accept New
* ON THE TABLE LOOT A PURPLE STONE! (TIMED QUEST)
* Move to CrossRoads!
steps.tips: * Make Sure you Hit lvl 11, 95% before cross the river

steps.description:
* move to Crossroads
* On the way Loot the the "Empty Keg"
* Accept the Item Keg Quest
steps.tips: * if the keg not there, don't worry move to XR anyway

steps.description:
* Accept Quests
* Sell your Goods and Resupply
* Bind your HS in CrossRoads
* Leave Nothway

* On the way North Kill Raptors + Plainstrider
* Climb the Mountain 
* Clear Cave Entrance on the Mountain 
* Go into the cave and use the Altar
* Go Down East ways
* Kill missing Striders
steps.tips: * Rar Mob very Dangerous, if your solo, skip quest!

steps.description:
* Kill All needed Razormanes
* If you don't have the empty Keg, Last Chance! (Accept Quest)
* Go Back To CrossRoads

* Turn In Quests 
* ACCEPT NEW ONE 
* Leave XR Eastway

* Accept BloodElves Quest
* Turn in Boulderslide
* Accept Elemental War
* Jump Down go to Inn, make it your HOME
* accept next to it Harpies Threaten
* Leave Sun Rock Retreat North way
steps.tips: * Do not accept Earthen Arise, waist of time!

steps.description:
* Loot Seeds on the Ground (BLUE)
* Kill everything (grinding)
* Kill Deers and loot eyes (do not complete, take what's there and go on)
* Grind your way North

* Go north
* Kill Deers, Loot Eyes (D)
* Kill Saps Loot Item (S)
* Kill Fey Dragon, Loot Item (RED, BLUE DOT)
* Kill Cats, Loot tail (T)
* Kill Cenarius Guys
* Grind your way back to Sun Rock Retreat

* There is a shortcut to sun Rock Retreat 
* Turn in and Accept Quest New Life
* Turn in and Accept Quest Ordanus
* Leave Sun Rock Retreat East
* go to Goblin Turn in Accept New Quest
* Go North

* Go north Look for XT4 and XT9, kill
* Move North
* Follow Mountain path until you find Gerenzo Wrenchwhistle
* Jump Down in Water
* Go back to Goblin to turn in Quest
steps.tips: * use "/tar xt" to find them!

steps.description:
* Go South East
* Turn in Quest and go on the small path to the barrens
* turn in Quest
* Hearthstone back to Sun Rock Retreat

* Kill Fire Elemental Loot Item
* harpy (H), Ambushers (A), Slayers (S), Roguefeathers (R)
* Plant seeds
* Go back to Sun Rock Retreat.
steps.tips: * Make sure you're least 5 bars (75%) away from 25.

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests
* ONLY accept "Calling in the Reserves"
* FLY to Thunderbluff

* IF YOU DONT have it already, TURN IN Elder Crone Quest
* Go to the Elders Rise Turn in Quest, Accept New
* Follow the "Vision" into OVER the bridge into the Spirit Rise Cave
* Turn in quest and Accept Tarren Mill Quest
* Accept Quest in front of the CHIEFTAIN
* Go to wind Rider -> camp Taurajo
steps.tips: * LEARN COOKING! REALLY IMPORTANT!

steps.description:
* Trun in "Ishamuhale" Accept Quest Thunder Lizards
* Accept (North Taurajo) "New Ore" Quest
* Make Taurajo your new Home
* Go South
* Kill ThinderLizards Loot Blood

* Look for Gann on the Street 
* turn in Quest / Accept New
* Loot Nitro and the other stuff,
* Go back to Gann, Turn in, Accept new Quest
* Go to the Flying Machine (south on the wooden tower) (Use item in inv, 30yards away)
* use it, 
* Go back to Gann
* Go South
steps.tips:
* Go south to the Tent accept quest, (GROUP QUEST)
* loot Crystal from a Chest into the Building (lvl30 NPC + 6 lvl 24) as Guards
* GRP QUEST: turn in Crystal at Tent
